   - Test on mobile viewport (< 768px) - sidebar should be fixed positioned
   - Test on tablet/desktop viewport (≥ 768px) - sidebar should be sticky

4. **Accessibility**
   - Navigate to toggle button using Tab key
   - Press Enter/Space to toggle
   - Verify screen reader announces button state (aria-expanded)
   - Check that all interactive elements have proper focus indicators

5. **Navigation Items**
